              <h2>How to use the Text Counter</h2>
              <p>
                This text counter is designed for writers, students, marketers,
                developers, and anyone who needs accurate word and character
                statistics. It updates in real time and works entirely in your
                browser.
              </p>
              <ol>
                <li>
